Some explanations:

so_files    - folder with files for shared object lib
test_files  - folder with test files  (test_1 ... test_4) 


MAKEFILE:    
            - make all
            - make clean
            - make run_all_tests
            - make run_test_1
            - make run_test_2
            - make run_test_3
            - make run_test_4

run_c.c     - main C functions
run_py.py   - python script